    <div class="fill-height">
      <ul class="text-lg" style="color: #cbd5e1;">
        <li><strong>$6.5 trillion</strong> tappable home equity available at 80% LTV threshold</li>
        <li>Borrowers prefer HELOCs to preserve sub-4% first-lien mortgage rates</li>
